{"tid":2215130,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"光大實業董事長涉違法違紀受查　 疑涉利益輸送　前副手同捲案","createTime":"2020-09-23T18:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T20:05:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91c8cde8b6b3baa06492ad73c38afc17d08f67e5","tid":2215130,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:49:17.000Z","msg":"中紀委昨公佈中國光大實業黨委書記、董事長兼總經理朱慧民涉嫌嚴重違紀違法，日前已被帶走調查。朱曾於光大銀行深圳分行擔任一把手七年之久，內媒引述消息指，朱被查主因涉任職光大銀行期間的問題，他當年的副手也被帶走調查。當局今次更罕有地借調黑龍江監察委員會協助調查，案件牽涉規模非比尋常。<br />\n<br />\n朱慧民入職光大實業前，曾於光大銀行工作多年，在鄭州、福州、深圳等城市的分行擔任一把手，其中在深圳分行就工作了七年之久。內媒《財新》引述知情人士透露，朱慧民本月10日被紀委人員從北京辦公室帶走。同日，朱以前在深圳的副手、現任浙商銀行深圳分行行長鄒建旭也被查，朱慧民一名同在浙商銀行深圳分行工作的姪兒則要求配合調查工作。有消息稱，鄒建旭被查時，其家也遭搜查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200924/BLESBNMHW5AE7O5SCU4CQ4TU3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200924%2FBLESBNMHW5AE7O5SCU4CQ4TU3E%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=51113dce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200924%2FBLESBNMHW5AE7O5SCU4CQ4TU3E%2F&h=8b4dbfc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200924/BLESBNMHW5AE7O5SCU4CQ4TU3E/</a>"},{"pid":"f20f784ad4cc426c64bb282f81144ad55a21ed43","tid":2215130,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"好嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e337baa8dd12380360c0af7798818e7343175a3f","tid":2215130,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6336d6cea1a58ce8345659e9056a8b6cc793af","tid":2215130,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:05:18.000Z","msg":"回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}